title: MIXI, Nazara & Google Play team up to launch ‘LVL Zero’ gaming incubator in India
description: MIXI Global Investments, Nazara Technologies, and ChimeraVC have launched the LVL Zero gaming incubator in India, backed by Google Play as Knowledge Partner. The program offers mentorship, funding, and global exposure to Indian gaming startups, aiming to support over 100 studios in the next five years.

title: Judge again bars Trump administration from deploying troops to Portland
